{"tid":106883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰：每次有警察同事被捕都傷心","createTime":"2017-02-04T04:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T18:12:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f4347b036536e3498b40967a3999dcc03b3244","tid":106883,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170204/s00001/1486176209324SL4_B17DA6DC15149DADA9D19B6ABB28B7F6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170204%2Fs00001%2F1486176209324SL4_B17DA6DC15149DADA9D19B6ABB28B7F6.jpg&h=fad871e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有警司涉貪被廉署拘捕，警務處長盧偉聰表示不評論案件，但強調警隊對於貪污行為心痛惡絕，若調查屬實，必定會「剷除這些壞分子」。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰在商台節目稱，警方對紀律操守十分重視，專業廉潔是警隊的核心價值，絕不容忍及姑息違法行為。他表示，由上世紀走過來，不容許有人破壞警隊辛苦建立的廉潔。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，沒有刻意隱瞞警員涉及違法行為的數字，去年被警方刑事拘捕的警員共21人，另外有6人和3人分別被廉署及海關拘捕，強調沒有以職業區分疑犯，亦不存在手軟放鬆。盧偉聰又說，警隊中99.8%同事正直誠實，每日都辛勤工作，但警隊是社會縮影，與其他部門機構一樣，不時有害群之馬，但強調「一個都嫌多」，每次有同事被捕都感到傷心。<br />\n<br />\n盧稱，警隊內部會加強教育及監督，希望同事不要容易受到誘惑，若有問題會嚴肅處理，以達到阻嚇警惕作用。"},{"pid":"cf71e8360304d0a99b57005a792ec1ae6bdcde7e","tid":106883,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:50:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00001/1486176293190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00001%2F1486176293190&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0093b817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170204%2Fs00001%2F1486176293190&h=c7925f0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170204/s00001/1486176293190</a>"},{"pid":"1968ac3b5be6484008d667329909f1e8d4016c01","tid":106883,"uid":56998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"最好係<br />\n每<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">次</span></span>有同事被捕都傷心"},{"pid":"c506fec3fa91654037a17ffb9950a6584f4cf8f4","tid":106883,"uid":56998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好係<br />\n每<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天</span></span>有同事被捕都傷心</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e31c3380c2313b324f7fc49bcc41b4785803dd8f","tid":106883,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:51:39.000Z","msg":"即係警察拉左個賊你就傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c72e7d58a2874da2e1ea3602f08b9ae037f72f4","tid":106883,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"休班警不能算警察&hellip;休班警。<br />\n休班警的事能算警察麼"},{"pid":"ccea87286ba2a42179b8333863a5647862fe63d0","tid":106883,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"咁應該傷心死"},{"pid":"7ecf737fc0799f95c08528cac68acf99f7bd2e21","tid":106883,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好係<br />\n每<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天</span></span>有同事被捕都傷心</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n根本就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca56317f3aa1fe93240be681fe3830033a44d23b","tid":106883,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"咁咪冇人用"},{"pid":"b47bff445a9a8ce67ac5053d93ec385501749f53","tid":106883,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:02:13.000Z","msg":"開心既高興既"},{"pid":"e75853bb866e8e0dbdef4ff3c50323261e800862","tid":106883,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:21:36.000Z","msg":"捉壞人梗喺傷心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，無得升職麻，用棍打就唔同呢，有退休金攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm